org.springframework.bootstrap
Interface SpringApplicationInitializer

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConfigFileApplicationContextInitializer, LoggingApplicationContextInitializer
public interface SpringApplicationInitializer

Strategy interface that can be used to initialize a SpringApplication before it is runs. A SpringApplicationInitializer can optionally implement EnvironmentAware if it needs to access or configure the underling application Environment.
